            <td valign="top" style="width: 225.25pt; border-right: 1pt inset; border-bottom: 1pt inset; border-left: 1pt inset; border-image: initial; border-top: none; padding: 0cm 5.4pt;">
            <p style="margin: 6pt 0cm; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="font-size: 7.5pt; letter-spacing: 0.3pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; color: black;">Train our staff</span></p>
            </td>
            <td valign="top" style="width: 225.25pt; border-top: none; border-left: none; border-bottom: 1pt inset; border-right: 1pt inset; padding: 0cm 5.4pt;">
            <p style="margin: 6pt 0cm; vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="font-size: 7.5pt; letter-spacing: 0.3pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; color: black;">So that, when you contact us, you get the best possible customer service</span></p>
            </td>
        </tr>
    </tbody>
</table>
