<p><strong></strong></p>
<strong>
<h2>What kind of communications does Bounty send?</h2>
</strong>
<p><strong></strong></p>
<p>If you joined Bounty and have said that we can contact you, we&rsquo;ll send you information by email, by app push notifications and / or through the post. The following section gives more detail of the types of information we will provide you with. </p>
<p><strong></strong></p>
<p><strong>Baby Development </strong><strong></strong></p>
<p>This popular, personalised weekly email series explains how your baby will grow and develop - and other useful parenting articles that we think you&rsquo;ll like and find helpful </p>
<p><strong>Bounty Offers &amp; Boutique</strong></p>
<p><strong></strong></p>
<p>Never miss an amazing offer &ndash; we&rsquo;ve got all the latest deals from the brands mums love and our own online shop </p>
<p><strong></strong></p>
<p><strong>Bounty News </strong></p>
<p>Get the latest updates on new features products and services that we&rsquo;ve been working on for you and notifications of when your next Bounty pack is ready to collect </p>
<p><strong></strong></p>
<p><strong>Bounty Portrait </strong><strong></strong></p>
<p>Receive special offers and find out how to order the beautiful newborn baby photos we take for you to treasure<strong> </strong><strong></strong></p>
<p> <strong>Bounty Partner promotions </strong></p>
<p>Bounty will send you emails with offers/ promotions on behalf of our carefully selected partners* related to: mother and baby and family products and services. We will never share your personal data with these partners </p>
<p><strong>By Post</strong></p>
<p>If you have opted to hear from us by post, we may post you a voucher for your free Growing Family Pack. The pack can also be claimed using the Bounty app. From time to time, we may post you money-off vouchers, news of retailers&rsquo; baby events and other family products and services e.g. financial services and family photography services<s>. </s></p>
<s><br />
</s><strong>
<h2>How can I see and update my information?</h2>
</strong>
<p>If you registered via the App or the Website, you can view, amend and/or delete any personal information you have provided us with at any time by editing Your Profile.</p>
<p>If you registered with the Bounty lady in hospital or using a registration card in your Pregnancy Information Folder, simply contact Customer Services on (03458) 300 200&nbsp;</p>
<p>Regardless of how you registered, all members can view and amend their communication preferences at any time by clicking the unsubscribe link at the bottom of any email from Bounty. &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>
<p><strong></strong></p>
<p>Please note that, as Bounty comprises a number of inter-connecting services, it might take a few days for all our systems to be updated, so you might get messages from us while we process your request.</p>
<p><strong></strong></p>
<p><strong></strong></p>
<strong>
<h2>What happens if I change my mind?</h2>
</strong>
<p><strong></strong></p>
<p>We make it easy for you to control your communication preferences or unsubscribe at any time</p>
<ol>
    <li>By clicking the unsubscribe option at the bottom of any email &ndash; this will give you the option to choose between unsubscribing from or</li>
    <li>Go to Bounty.com and log in via the button in the top right of the screen. Use the same email address and password as the one you used to register or log in on the App. Once logged in, edit your profile by clicking on your user name in the top right corner. You can then amend your contact preferences or</li>
    <li>Within the 'My Profile' section of the App, go to 'edit details' and select 'no' to receiving free samples and offers or</li>
    <li>Telephone Customer Services (03458) 300 200</li>
</ol>
<p>Please note that, as Bounty comprises a number of inter-connecting services, it might take a few days for all our systems to be updated, so you might get messages from us while we process your request.</p>
<p> </p>
<strong>
<h2>Keeping your information</h2>
</strong>
<p><strong></strong></p>
<p>As a pregnancy and parenting club we provide information about products and services relevant to pregnant women and women with children up to the age of five and will therefore retain your information until your child reaches the age of 5. If you have shared information about multiple children in your family, we will continue to share information with you about products and services that are relevant to each child until the youngest child reaches the age of five. </p>
<p>During this time, in addition to communications relevant to having children of a certain age, we will also continue to send you information about you as a woman and parent, as well as whole family related communications (e.g. family friendly holidays) unless of course you tell us that you no longer wish to be a member of Bounty or you unsubscribe from specific communications.&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>
<p><strong></strong></p>
<p>In the case of any contact you may have with our Customer Services team, we will retain your information for as long as is necessary to provide support or support-related reporting and trend analysis only.</p>
<p><br />
</p>
<strong>
<h2>Security</h2>
</strong>
<p>The security of your personal information is very important to us, and we take all reasonable steps to protect your personal information.&nbsp; We cannot guarantee the security of any personal information you disclose online and any transmission of your personal information is at your own risk. You accept the inherent security implications of providing information online and will not hold us responsible for any breach of security unless we have been negligent or in wilful default.</p>
<br />
<strong>
<h2>How to Contact Us</h2>
</strong>
<p> If you:</p>
<ul>
    <li>Have any questions or feedback about this notice</li>
    <li>Would like us to stop using your information</li>
    <li>Want to exercise any of your rights as set out above, or have a complaint</li>
</ul>
<p>please don&rsquo;t hesitate to contact us and we will be happy to answer any questions you may have.</p>
<p><strong>Customer Services</strong> - (03458) 300 200&nbsp;</p>
<p><strong>Privacy Team</strong> - <a href="mailto:privacy@bounty.com">privacy@bounty.com</a> </p>
<p><strong>Write to us:<br />
</strong>Bounty (UK) Limited<br />
29 Broadwater Road<br />
Welwyn Garden City<br />
AL7 3BQ</p>
